🎤 Interview Questions
Q1

Why verify that the service was not called?

Answer

Because validation should reject invalid requests before reaching the business logic. This prevents unnecessary processing and database access.

Q2

Why test validation separately?

Answer

Validation is the first layer of defense. If validation breaks, invalid data can reach the service layer and cause inconsistent application state.


