Q2
Why store logs in a file?

Answer

Console logs disappear after restart.

Files can be analyzed later for debugging and monitoring.

Q3
Why use a custom stream?

Answer

Morgan generates request logs, while Winston manages where and how logs are stored. A custom stream connects the two.


